article_title: Who Was the Most-Searched Star of 2013?
article_text:
Who was the most-searched star on Yahoo this year? The site released their Year In Review report today, rounding up the top stories and trends of 2013 based on the search habits of millions of users. Click through to see the overall top-searched people and topics!

Above: Justin Bieber squeaked in at number 10 this year. The 19-year-old pop star’s next album, Believe 3D, will have a limited release on Christmas day.
